race.comment: FAST HARRY (1) made it a hat-trick last start at Northam when gunning down his rivals as a $1.28 fave at Northam last start. He looks a horse better than this grade, though he will be a long way back from the draw. He looks above average however, and Pike can work him to the outside where he can swoop late. SOLDANELLE (2) jumped favourite last start in a better race and is on the quick turnaround. Parnham hops in the saddle now and she draws a much better gate this time around. Can sit closer this time and will be hard to hold out. HEWILLDOUS (6) got back to winning ways here on Cup Day when beating what looks a progressive type. He looks an improving type and that rating stacks up in this grade. Can feature in the finish. PURE OBSESSION (7) got the job done at Belmont 24 days ago and the form out of that race has been very strong. Has to be included. ASTRO WORLD (11) is better than she showed last time out and can improve with Parnham replacing the apprentice hoop.
